sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as AI Gateway<br/>Istio/Envoy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ExtProc as ext_proc Service<br/>9004/TCP gRPC
    participant HeadersGuard as maas-headers-guard
    participant Resolver as model-provider-resolver
    participant Translation as api-translation
    participant KeyInjection as apikey-injection
    participant Provider as External LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{ns}/{model}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Gateway-level auth<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>ExtProc: ext_proc request headers+body<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, mTLS (Istio)

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over ExtProc,KeyInjection: Request Plugin Pipeline (in-process)
        ExtProc->>HeadersGuard: Process request
        HeadersGuard-->>ExtProc: Strip x-maas-* headers
        ExtProc->>Resolver: Resolve model
        Resolver-->>ExtProc: Provider info from CRD cache<br/>(endpoint, auth, API format)
        ExtProc->>Translation: Translate request
        Translation-->>ExtProc: Convert to provider format<br/>(OpenAI→Anthropic/Azure/Bedrock/Vertex)
        ExtProc->>KeyInjection: Inject credentials
        KeyInjection-->>ExtProc: Add auth headers from Secret cache<br/>(Bearer/x-api-key/api-key/SigV4)
    end

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: Mutated headers + body
    Gateway->>Provider: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>(via ExternalName Svc → ServiceEntry → DestinationRule)
    Provider-->>Gateway: Provider response
    Gateway->>ExtProc: ext_proc response headers+body<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, mTLS (Istio)

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over ExtProc,Translation: Response Plugin Pipeline (in-process)
        ExtProc->>Translation: Translate response
        Translation-->>ExtProc: Convert to OpenAI format<br/>(strip provider-specific fields)
    end

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: Mutated response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 2: ExternalProvider Reconciliation

    participant User as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EPCtrl as ExternalProvider<br/>Controller

    User->>K8sAPI: Create ExternalProvider CR<br/>HTTPS/443, User RBAC
    K8sAPI->>EPCtrl: Watch event<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    EPCtrl->>K8sAPI: Validate referenced Secret<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    EPCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ExternalName Service<br/>(points to provider FQDN)
    EPCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Istio ServiceEntry<br/>(MESH_EXTERNAL, DNS)
    EPCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create DestinationRule<br/>(tls.mode: SIMPLE)

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 3: ExternalModel Reconciliation

    participant EMCtrl as ExternalModel<br/>Controller

    User->>K8sAPI: Create ExternalModel CR<br/>HTTPS/443, User RBAC
    K8sAPI->>EMCtrl: Watch event<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    EMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Get ExternalProvider CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    EMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create/Update HTTPRoute<br/>(path-prefix + header match,<br/>timeout: 300s)
